snippet.title: Ping!
snippet.description:
haha gotem. Watch Ping 2! I just dropped it last month: https://youtu.be/8CYy9jNmpXM

-

To this day, this is my most legendary piece, kickstarting my career from nothing! Tried to troll ppl with the use of discord sounds, combining it with my style of music to weave in cool riffs and clean mixing. I am extremely grateful to all of you guys for the support, it came at a dark time in my life when I was seriously doubting pursuing music anymore. Special thanks to Zencha, a former staff member at Discord, who picked my song as a honorable mention in the Discord Hackweek 2019 contest. Without his seemingly insignificant decision, the YouTube algorithm would have never noticed me. Lastly, I really want you guys to watch ping 2, I've been working on it for a very long time and I truly think it lives up to the beast that this song was! Watch here https://youtu.be/8CYy9jNmpXM

#Exyl #FLUTEGANG
